Description:
Gain &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;grit&lt;/font&gt; while performing Crosscut.&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;

(Grit prevents you from being staggered by incoming attacks.)&lt;/font&gt;

In &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;defiant stance&lt;/font&gt;, gain &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;stun immunity&lt;/font&gt; while performing Crosscut.

Swing up in a brutal arc, &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;staggering&lt;/font&gt; your target, dealing &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.Greatsword_DefenseBreak1.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_slash_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage and applying &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;2&lt;/font&gt; stacks of &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Greatsword_Stacking_Rend.PhysicalArmor * -100]}% &lt;/font&gt; &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;rend&lt;/font&gt; for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Greatsword_Stacking_Rend.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt;. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Max {[Type_StatusEffectData.Greatsword_Stacking_Rend.StackMax]} stacks.)&lt;/font&gt;

In &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;onslaught stance&lt;/font&gt; apply &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;1&lt;/font&gt; additional &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;rend&lt;/font&gt;.

Enter &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;onslaught stance&lt;/font&gt; when the upward arc of this ability ends.

Hitting foes reduces greatsword &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;cooldowns&lt;/font&gt;:
•Light attack: &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[GreatswordAbilityTable.Ultimate_Greatsword_Offense.CooldownTimer * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt;
•Charged heavy attack: &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[GreatswordAbilityTable.Helper_Ultimate_Greatsword_Offense_1.CooldownTimer * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;

(Cooldown reduction only occurs once per attack.)&lt;/font&gt;

Block for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;2s&lt;/font&gt; while reducing block stamina damage taken by &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[GreatswordAbilityTable.Helper_Greatsword_Counter_BlockStability.BlockDamageReduction * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt;, then unleash a counterattack that strikes all foes within a &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;4m&lt;/font&gt; radius.

•No Blocks: &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.Greatsword_Counter.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_slash_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage.
•1 Block: &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.Greatsword_Counter_1.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_slash_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage and &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;staggers&lt;/font&gt;.
•2 Blocks: &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.Greatsword_Counter_2.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_slash_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage and &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;staggers&lt;/font&gt; longer.
•3 Blocks: &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.Greatsword_Counter_3.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_slash_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage and causes a &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;knockback&lt;/font&gt;.

This ability has &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;grit&lt;/font&gt;.&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt; (Grit prevents you from being staggered by incoming attacks.)&lt;/font&gt;

Reactivate this ability or use basic attack to counterattack earlier.

Enter &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;defiant stance&lt;/font&gt; when the counterattack of this ability ends.&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;

Taunt Gem Compatible: If you have a Carnelian gem equipped in your greatsword, activating this ability inflicts taunt for {[DamageTable.OH_Shield_FinalStand.TauntDuration]}s to all enemies within 8m. (Taunt causes monsters to focus only on you.)&lt;/font&gt;

Counter attack &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;crit chance&lt;/font&gt; is increased by &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[GreatswordAbilityTable.Upgrade_Greatsword_Counter_2.CritChance * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt;.

In &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;onslaught stance&lt;/font&gt;, the counter attack gains an additional &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[GreatswordAbilityTable.Helper_Greatsword_Counter_BonusCrit.CritChance * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; critical hit chance.

In &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;defiant stance&lt;/font&gt;, the counter attack &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;heals&lt;/font&gt; for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[GreatswordAbilityTable.Helper_Greatsword_Counter_BonusLifesteal.DmgPctToHealth * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; of its damage. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Max {[GreatswordAbilityTable.Helper_Greatsword_Counter_BonusLifesteal.NumberOfTrackedHits]} hits.)&lt;/font&gt;

Stab the ground and send out a shockwave with a &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[SpellDataTable_Greatsword.Spell_Ability_Greatsword_Burst.Radius]}m&lt;/font&gt; radius that deals &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.Greatsword_Burst.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_strike_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage. Gain &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Greatsword_Stacking_Fortify.PhysicalArmor * 100]}% &lt;/font&gt; &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;fortify&lt;/font&gt; for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Greatsword_Stacking_Fortify.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt; for each foe hit. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Max {[Type_StatusEffectData.Greatsword_Stacking_Fortify.StackMax]} stacks.)&lt;/font&gt;

This ability generates &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.Greatsword_Burst_Push.ThreatMultiplier * 100]}% &lt;/font&gt; &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;threat&lt;/font&gt; and has &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;grit&lt;/font&gt;.&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt; (Grit prevents you from being staggered by incoming attacks.)&lt;/font&gt;

Enter &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;defiant stance&lt;/font&gt; when this ability ends.&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;

Taunt Gem Compatible: If you have a Carnelian gem equipped in your greatsword, this ability inflicts taunt for {[DamageTable.Greatsword_Burst.TauntDuration]}s to all enemies hit. (Taunt causes monsters to focus only on you.)&lt;/font&gt;

After completing any ability in the Onslaught tree, enter &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;onslaught stance&lt;/font&gt; for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Greatsword_Stance_Offense.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt;.

Onslaught stance has the following properties:
•&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Outgoing Damage&lt;/font&gt; Increased: &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Greatsword_Stance_Offense.DMGStandard * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt;
•&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Damage Taken&lt;/font&gt; Increased: &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Greatsword_Stance_Offense.WKNStandard * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt;
•&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Quick Charge&lt;/font&gt;: Heavy attacks charge &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;50% faster&lt;/font&gt; but consume &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[StaminaCosts_Player.Greatsword_Offense_Attack.StaminaCost]} stamina&lt;/font&gt; each

&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Entering defiant stance or switching weapons will immediately end onslaught stance.)&lt;/font&gt;

After completing any ability in the Defiance tree, enter &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;defiant stance&lt;/font&gt; for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Greatsword_Stance_Defense.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt;.

Defiant stance has the following properties:
•&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Damage Taken&lt;/font&gt; Reduced: &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Greatsword_Stance_Defense.WKNStandard * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt;
•&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Outgoing Damage&lt;/font&gt; Reduced: &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Greatsword_Stance_Defense.DMGStandard * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt;
•&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Guard Point&lt;/font&gt;: Block incoming attacks while charging heavy attacks &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;

(Entering onslaught stance or switching weapons will immediately end defiant stance.)&lt;/font&gt;
